embeds.description:
Welcome to the Managers & Mods Area.

This private section will include people like members of the Executive Board, Section Managers, past managers, committee members, moderators,  and others that are here to help with general leadership both here on discord, and outside in the guidance and execution of roles in VES itself.

Feel free to use the Section channels to work with and communicate with your various groups. As with the members-only channels, I feel that keeping the permissions so that these channels aren't walled will greatly help with sub-section leadership and the maintenance of institutional knowledge withing VES at large.
